<center> <h2>A warm welcome to four AI4SMM postdoctoral fellows</h2> </center>
<center> <h1>AI4SMM Research</h1> </center>

<p>Early 2023, the AI4SMM call for research proposals for postdoctoral fellowship projects 
was concluded and four excellent multidisciplinary projects were awarded. 
We are very happy that we can now welcome our first AI4SMM postdoctoral fellows to the lab:</p>

